Welcome to SalesManagementApp’s documentation!¶

SalesManagementApp is a sample project developed in the subject of Software Quality in order to learn how to improve and mantain the code, use tools like code inspectors, CI tools, etc.

#Project status The project version is v0.2 and it’s still under development
